rows.label: xs33580100_MSG0010
rows.name: Oh, phew! You're still in one piece![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33580100_MSG0020
rows.name:
I came to right over here,
and was trying to figure out how best to proceed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33580100_MSG0030
rows.name:
In the end, I decided to pop a flare and sit tight,
just like my brother taught me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33580100_MSG0050
rows.name: I guess it's a little premature to be celebrating, huh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33580100_MSG0060
rows.name:
Anyway, you can count on me.
I've still got some fight left in me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33580100_MSG0070
rows.name: I'll back you up with everything I've got![ST:wait ]
